("00-charter.md","Program charter","Build an independent browser engine and product as a measured research program, not a parity claim.","Mission and principles|Independence boundary|Evidence before claims|User safety and reversibility","Charter accepted; scope and non-goals are versioned.","Ambition outruns evidence."),
("01-product-requirements.md","Product requirements","Treat requirements as stable identifiers with measurable acceptance criteria and phase ownership.","Everyday browsing|Developer-first workflows|Thirty-tab behavior|AI assistance|Release evidence","All 46 requirements are indexed and no milestone lacks metrics.","Vague goals cannot gate releases."),
